# 3. hashCode() Method

## Purpose

Returns unique integer value for object.

## Syntax

```java
public int hashCode()
```

## Example

```java
class Demo {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Demo d = new Demo();

        System.out.println(d.hashCode());
    }
}
```

